{"tid":2045291,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"原來人，真係好化學","createTime":"2020-05-31T17:00:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T10:42:23.000Z","uid":187192,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1f62bddc21c9f67f487d3be246b8dbf7d1d234b5","tid":2045291,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"中學畢左業幾年 大家各散東西 <br />\n有d為事業打併 有d為生活忙碌<br />\n偶爾有人結婚會先會聚一聚<br />\n<br />\n喂 佢唔得啦 快d黎醫院見下佢啦<br />\n<br />\n佢開始有病 到今日都只係1年都唔夠<br />\n<br />\n一入到病房 佢唔再係曾經認識又肥又可愛既肥仔<br />\n而係瘦到見骨 塊面只係得返雙眼同顴骨...<br />\n難以想像佢呢一年經歷過既痛苦<br />\n雖然我當下真係好無言好無耐 唔知做咩好 但佢依然係最善良 最真實 仲會關心我地既佢 <br />\n<br />\n因為已經走到尾聲 打左嗎啡後醫生話呢個係彌留狀態 ...可能只係得返最後今晚<br />\n<br />\n希望你可以去一個再無痛苦既世界 你永遠都係我地既好朋友<br />\n<br />\n同時亦希望大家珍惜眼前人 祝願大家身體健康"},{"pid":"0200b1cf8adb2c88c90b7c3eed0396174d5edcc5","tid":2045291,"uid":66817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:05:42.000Z","msg":"咩病？"},{"pid":"eeb70eac3856cfcffb150ecbc46b262c77bafb8f","tid":2045291,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"咩病"},{"pid":"ba384dbea1cb876db0ce71ebf9478154e6d9ecaa","tid":2045291,"uid":187192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:06:10.000Z","msg":"腸癌"},{"pid":"791f2215eeaac2f9edd768cb1e4b871c9cb22fe4","tid":2045291,"uid":155225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:10:01.000Z","msg":"佢幾歲"},{"pid":"3c739f0eccc36b97ee1bfa26f223d6dde717d4ff","tid":2045291,"uid":187192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:10:54.000Z","msg":"中學畢業無耐 廿幾"},{"pid":"a015b53ac9e3998d9d175e81d835a92b2cbcb0f8","tid":2045291,"uid":18265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip 大家珍惜身邊人吖"},{"pid":"cd71e4a0e7d12b7e7105b1b67bc545c3d066348c","tid":2045291,"uid":54328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":